Output docs/demo-history.gif

Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Width 1920
Set Height 1080
Set FontSize 24
Set Framerate 60
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set Padding 20
Set PlaybackSpeed 1

Sleep 500ms
Type "zlib history"
Sleep 300ms
Enter

# Wait for API + book detail fetch
Sleep 4s

# Browse history items
Down
Sleep 400ms
Down
Sleep 400ms
Down
Sleep 600ms
Down
Sleep 400ms
Down
Sleep 400ms
Down
Sleep 5s

Escape
Sleep 500ms
